#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:4
msgid "Mirror Modifier"
msgstr "镜像修改器--knight翻译"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:9
msgid "The corner of a cube mirrored across three axes to form... well... a cube."
msgstr "一个立方体的一角沿着三个轴向作镜像，构成另一个立方体。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:12
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Mirror modifier mirrors a mesh along its *local* X-, Y- and/or "
"Z-Axes, across the object's center (the mirror plane is then defined by "
"the two other axes)."
msgstr "镜像修改器沿着自己 **局部** X，Y和、或Z轴镜像，横穿物体的中心（镜面用其他两个轴定义的）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:15
msgid ""
"It can also use another object as the mirror center, then use that "
"object's local axes instead of its own."
msgstr "它也可以用其他物体作为镜像中心，接着用那个物体的局部坐标轴，而不是自己的局部坐标轴。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:19
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:23
#, fuzzy
msgid "Mirror modifier."
msgstr "镜像修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:34
msgid "Axis"
msgstr "轴"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:27
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The X-, Y-, Z-axis along which to mirror (i.e. the axis perpendicular to "
"the mirror plane of symmetry)."
msgstr "沿着镜像的轴 (*X*、*Y* 或 *Z*) （即，该轴垂直于对称的镜面）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:30
msgid ""
"To understand how the axis applies to the mirror direction, if you were "
"to mirror on the X axis, the positive X values of the original mesh would"
" become the negative X values on the mirrored side."
msgstr "为了明白轴是如何应用到镜像的方向上的，如果你想要在X轴上镜像，原始网面的正X值将会在镜像的一侧变成负X值。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:33
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can select more than one of these axes - you will then get more "
"mirrored copies. With one axis you get a single mirror, with two axes "
"four mirrors, and with all three axes eight mirrors."
msgstr "你可以选择多个轴——随之得到更多的镜像。一个轴得到一个镜像，两个轴得到四个镜像，所有的三个轴得到八个镜像。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:62
msgid "Options:"
msgstr "选项："

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:39
msgid "Merge"
msgstr "合并"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:38
msgid ""
"Where a vertex is in the same place (within the *Merge Limit* distance) "
"as its mirror it will be merged with the mirrored vertex."
msgstr "作为镜像并在同一个位置的顶点（在 *合并限度* 距离之内），它将与镜像顶点合并。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:52
msgid "Clipping"
msgstr "裁剪"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:42
msgid ""
"Prevents vertices from moving through the mirror plane(s) while the user "
"is transforming them in Edit Mode."
msgstr "用户在编辑模式下工作时，阻止顶点穿过镜面。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:44
msgid ""
"If *Clipping* is enabled but vertices are beyond the mirror plane and "
"outside of the *Merge Limit*, the vertices will not be merged. But as "
"soon as the vertices are within *Merge Limit* they are snapped together "
"and cannot be moved beyond the mirror plane."
msgstr ""
"如果已启用 *裁剪* 选项，但顶点超出了镜面且在 *合并限制* 之外，顶点是不会合并的。但只要顶点是在 *合并限制* "
"之内，它们会吸附在一起，且不能穿越镜子到另一边。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:50
msgid ""
"Vertices on the mirror plane will be unable to move away from the mirror "
"plane as long as *Clipping* is enabled. You must disable *Clipping* to be"
" able to move the vertices along the mirror axis again."
msgstr "只要启用了 *裁剪* 选项，镜面上的顶点将无法移离镜面。你必须禁用 *裁剪* 选项才能沿镜轴移动顶点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:62
msgid "Vertex Groups"
msgstr "顶点组"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:55
msgid ""
"When enabled, the Mirror modifier will try to mirror existing vertex "
"groups."
msgstr "当启用该选项时，镜像修改器会尝试镜像现有的顶点组。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:57
msgid "A very nice feature, but one that has very specific prerequisites:"
msgstr "它是一款很不错的功能，且有着很特殊的先决条件："

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:59
msgid ""
"The vertex groups you want to mirror must be named following the usual "
"left/right pattern (i.e. suffixed by something like \".R\", \".right\", "
"\".L\", etc)."
msgstr "镜像的顶点组必须按照常规的左/右模式来命名（即以 “.R”，“.ri​​ght”，“.L”等为后缀）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:61
msgid ""
"The mirror side vertex group must already exist (it will not be created "
"automatically). It must also be completely empty (no vertices assigned to"
" it)."
msgstr "镜面一边的顶点组必须已经存在（它不会自动创建）。它也必须是完全空的（没有分配顶点给它）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:69
msgid "Textures"
msgstr "纹理"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:65
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The U and V options allows you to mirror the UV texture coordinates "
"across the middle of the image."
msgstr "*U* 和 *V* 选项可以让你以图像的中间来镜像UV纹理坐标。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:68
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"E.g. if you have a vertex with UV coordinates of (0.3, 0.9), its mirror "
"copy will have UV coordinates of (0.7, 0.1)."
msgstr "例如，如果你顶点的UV坐标是(``0.3, 0.9``)，它的镜像副本的UV坐标将会是(``0.7, 0.1``)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:73
msgid "Merge Limit"
msgstr "合并限度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:72
msgid ""
"The maximum distance between a vertex and its mirror copy before they are"
" merged together. In other words, a vertex may be half this distance away"
" from the mirror plane before it snaps to it."
msgstr "顶点与其镜像副本在合并到一起前，它们之间的最大距离。换言之，顶点在吸附到镜面上前，可以离镜面有一半的该距离。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:79
msgid "Mirror Object"
msgstr "镜像物体"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:76
msgid ""
"The name of another object (usually an empty), to be used as the "
"reference for the mirror process: its center and axes will drive the "
"plane(s) of symmetry. You can of course animate its position/rotation to "
"animate the mirror effect."
msgstr "另一个物体的名称（通常是空物体），供镜像过程参考：其中心和轴将沿着平面（一个或多个）作对称。你当然可以修改其位置/旋转属性，以观看动态的镜面效果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:82
msgid "Hints"
msgstr "提示"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:84
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Many modeling tasks involve creating objects that are symmetrical. "
"However, there used to be no quick way to model both halves of an object "
"without using one of the workarounds that have been discovered by clever "
"Blender artists over the years. A common technique was to model one half "
"of an object and use :kbd:`Alt-D` to create a linked duplicate which can "
"then be scaled on one axis by −1 to produce a perfect mirror-image copy "
"which updates in real time as you edit."
msgstr ""
"很多建模任务都涉及到创建对称的物体。然而，在没有被聪明的Blender艺术家多年来发现了一种变通方案之前，过去没有快速建模对象两半的方法。一个常见的​​技巧是建模一半物体，然后使用"
" :kbd:`Alt-D` 创建链接副本，随后可以通过在其中一个轴上缩放 ``-1`` 以产生完美的镜像副本，它可以在你编辑的时候实时更新。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:90
msgid ""
"The Mirror modifier offers a simpler way to do this. Once your modeling "
"is completed you can either click *Apply* to make a real version of your "
"mesh or leave it as is for future editing."
msgstr "镜像修改器提供了一个简单的方法来做到这一点。一旦你建模完成后，可以点击 *应用*，观看网面的真实版本，或者保持不变，以供将来编辑。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:95
msgid "Using the Mirror Modifier with a Subdivision Surface Modifier"
msgstr "镜像修改器与细分表面修改器的配合使用"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:97
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When using the Mirror modifier along with a :doc:`subsurf "
"</modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>` modifier, the order in which the "
"modifiers are placed is important."
msgstr "镜像修改器同 :doc:`细分表面 </modifiers/generate/subsurf>` 修改器一起使用时，其中，修改器的顺序很重要。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:104
#, fuzzy
msgid "Subsurf modifier before Mirror modifier."
msgstr "细分表面修改器在镜像修改器之前"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:107
msgid ""
"The above image shows the subsurf modifier placed before the Mirror one; "
"as you can see the effect of this is that the mesh is split down the "
"center line of the mirror effect. This is because the subsurf calculation"
" moves vertices away from the mirror plane, too far away from the *Merge "
"Limit*."
msgstr ""
"上图显示了细分表面修改器置于镜面修改器前的效果；你可以看到这样的效果，网面沿着中心线分割的镜像效果。这是因为，细分表面修改器的计算移动顶点远离镜面，远在"
" *合并限度* 之外。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:116
#, fuzzy
msgid "Mirror modifier before Subsurf modifier."
msgstr "镜像修改器在细分表面修改器之前"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:119
msgid ""
"The above image shows the Mirror modifier placed before the subsurf "
"modifier. In this order, the mirror calculation is done and the vertices "
"are merged together. Only after that does the subsurf modifier move any "
"vertices."
msgstr "上图显示了镜像修改器置于细分表面修改器之前的效果。在此顺序里，镜像的计算完成后，顶点被合并在一起。只有在那之后，细分表面修改器会移动任何顶点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:125
msgid "Accurately Positioning the Mirror Plane"
msgstr "精确定位镜面"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:127
msgid ""
"To apply a Mirror modifier, it is common to have to move the object's "
"center onto the edge or face that is to be the axis for mirroring. This "
"can be tricky when attempted visually."
msgstr "应用镜像修改器之前，需要移动物体的中心到边或面，以此作为镜像的轴。视觉上尝试时难以捉摸。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:131
msgid ""
"A good technique to achieve an exact position is to select the edge, then"
" use :kbd:`Shift-S` and choosing *Cursor to Selection*. This will "
"position the 3D Cursor in the center of the edge. Finally, press :kbd"
":`Ctrl-Alt-Shift-C` for the *Set Origin* menu, then select *Origin to 3D "
"Cursor*. This will move the object's center (and thus, the mirror plane) "
"to where the 3D cursor is located, and the mirroring will be exact."
msgstr ""
"完成精准定位的一个好技巧是选择边，然后使用 :kbd:`Shift-S` 并选择 *移动光标到选择* 。这将在边的中心放置3D光标。最后，按下 "
":kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Shift-C` 唤出 *设置原点* 菜单，然后选择 "
"*移动原点到3D光标*。这将移动物体的中心（也就是镜面）到3D光标的位置，镜像操作将是精准的。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:139
msgid ""
"An alternative is to use an Empty as a *Mirror Object* that you move to "
"the correct position."
msgstr "另一种方法是使用一个空物体，作为你移动到正确位置的 *镜物体*。"

